/~/media/HelpCenter/Documents/tv/dish/dish-channel-guide.ashx?la=en|title=Dish Channel Guide.|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>|| If Yes, this channel offers secondary audio programming to providers, this usually contains either audio description or a Spanish language dub.\n|-\n| [[Nielsen ratings|Households]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/features/overcrowded-cable-sector-esquire-spike-fyi-1202012647/|title=Variety - PDF halfway down the page entitled Net Worth.|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>|| The total number of households with viewing access to the channel (Not including households where the channel is available but not subscribed to).\n|}\n\n=== English Language ===\n{| class=\"toccolours sortable\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; font-size:90%; text-align:center; width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | Genre\n! style=\"width:12%;\" | Name\n! style=\"width:20%;\" | Owner (Subsidary)\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | Launch \nDate\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | OTA\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | East/\nWest\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | HD\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | VOD\n! style=\"width:5%;\" | SAP\n! style=\"width:8%;\" | Households\n! style=\"width:25%;\" | Notes\n|-\n! rowspan=\"38\" | Variety\n|[[A&E (TV channel)|A&E]]||[[The Walt Disney Company]] [50%] / [[Hearst Communications]] [50%] ([[A&E Networks]]) || 1984\n|  - || Yes || Yes || Yes || -\n| 90,343,000 || Launched as Arts & Entertainment Network / 1995 as A&E Network. Formed by merger of 'ARTS' and 'The Entertainment Channel' in 1984\n|-\n|[[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]||[[The Walt Disney Company]] ([[Walt Disney Television]]) || 1948\n|Yes|| Yes || Yes || - || Yes\n|114,848,000||[[Big Four Television Networks|Major commercial network]]\n|-\n|[[Aspire (TV network)|Aspire]]|| Magic Johnson Enterprises || 2012\n|  -|| - || Yes || - || -\n| || \n|-\n|[[AWE 